    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Occult initiates are the most recent inductees into their organization and the members of the organization most often encountered by outsiders.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"387\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Occultists of the Vermilion Dream</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[â€“]</span></span></h2> <p>The Consortium of the Vermilion Dream is viewed as an esoteric, profit-driven, but ultimately harmless cabal of ghost hunters and perpetuators of urban legends. This perception isn't inaccurate, but the consortium's leadership is obsessed with one set of legends in particular: those involving the Moon of Ill Omen, Ruidus, and the ancient figures cursed by exposure to its alien influence.</p><p>The cruelest desires and predilections of the consortium's most obsessive agents have been enhanced by contact with ruidium-tainted items.</p></div></div>",
